    <h1 id="lumasense-title">Official Announcement from LumaSense™</h1>
    <p class="site-intro">Via our retained thought-partner, Big Charli’s Blind Marketing Consultancy™</p>
    <p><em>“They’ll never see you coming.”™</em></p>

